Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:17.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I feel that the wind is bringing change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:18.33,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}何かが変わりそうな気がしているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:22.77,OP,,0,0,0,,I guess that's your fault for calling out to my heart
