Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:38.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Spread our wings with more courage than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:38.51,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}手を伸ばそう　いつよりも力強い勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:42.96,OP,,0,0,0,,Light and dark are still vague in the distance
