Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:53.80,OP,,0,0,0,,No one so far has ever reached
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:54.18,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今は誰の名前でもない
